response.original_title: Frank Mills: The Music of Frank Mills
response.overview: Music & Musicals, Pop, Rock & Pop - With two No. 1 singles under his belt, pianist Frank Mills is no stranger to the popular charts, having composed the international instrumental hit "Music Box Dancer." This collection celebrates the unmistakable talent of a timeless musician. Tracks include "The Peter Piper Theme," "Seascapes," "The Blues Don't Last," "Jingle Bells," "Chickadee," "What Child Is This," "Away in a Manger," "Music Box Child," "Flat Baroque" and more.
